quran[24]{c,v,t}:
  42,27,Agar Allah Taalaa apnay (sab) bandon ki rozi faraakh ker deta to woh zamin mein fasad barpa ker detay lekin woh andazay kay sath jo kuch chahata hai nazil farmata hai woh apnay bandon say poora khabardar hai aur khoob dekhney wala hai
  42,28,Aur wohi hai jo logon kay na-umeed hojaney kay bad barish barsata hai aur apni rehmat phela deta hai. Wohi hai kaar saaz aur qabil-e-hamd-o-sana
  42,29,Aur uss ki nishaniyon mein say aasmano aur zamin ki pedaeesh hai aur inn mein jandaron ka phelana hai. Woh iss per bhi qadir hai kay jab chahye unhen jama ker day
  42,30,Tumhen jo kuch museebaten phonchti hai woh tumharay apnay hathon kay kartoot ka badla hai aur woh to boht si baton say darguzar farma deta hai
  42,31,Aur tum humen zamin mein aajiz kerney walay nahi ho tumharay liye siwaye Allah Taalaa kay na koi kaar saaz hai na madadgar
  42,32,Aur darya mein chalney wali paharon jaisi kashtiyan uss ki nishaniyon mein say hain
  42,33,Agar woh chahye to hawa band kerday aur yeh kashtiyan samnadaron per ruki reh jayen. Yaqeenan iss mein jer sabar kerney walay shukar guzar kay liye nishaniyan hain
  42,34,Ya enhen inn kay kartootton kay baees tabah kerday woh to boht si khataon say darguzar farmaya kerta hai
  42,35,Aur takay jo log humari nishaniyon mein jhagartay hain woh maloom kerlen kay unn kay liye chutkara nahi
  42,36,To tumhen jo kuch diya gaya hai woh zindaganiy-e-duniya ka kuch yun hi sa asbab hai aur Allah kay pass jo hai woh iss say ba-darja behtar aur payedaar hai woh unn kay liye hai jo eman laye aur sirf apnay rab hi per bharosa rakhtay hain
  42,37,Aur kabeerah gunahon say aur be-hayaeeon say bachtay hain aur gussay kay waqt (bhi) maaf ker detay hain
  42,38,Aur apnay rab kay farman ko qabool kertay hain aur unn ka (her) kaam aapas kay mashwaray say hota hai aur jo hum ney unhen dey rakha hai uss mein say (humaray naam per) detay hain
  42,39,Aur jab unn per zulm-(o-ziyadti) hoto woh sirf badla ley letay hain
  42,40,Aur baraee ka badla ussi jaisi buraee hai aur jo maaf ker dayaur islah kerley uss ka ajar Allah kay zimay hai (fil-waqey) Allah Taalaa zalimon say mohabbat nahi kerta
  42,41,Aur jo shaks apnay mazloom honay kay baad (barabar ka) badla ley ley to aisay logon per (ilzam ka) koi raasta nahi
  42,42,Yeh raasta sirf unn logon per hai jo khud doosron per zulm keren aur zamin mein na haq fasad kertay phiren yehi log hain jinn kay liye dard-naak azab hai
  42,43,Aur jo shaks sabar kerley aur maaf kerdey yaqeenan yeh bari himmat kay kaamon mein say (aik kaam) hai
  42,44,Aur jissay Allah Taalaa behka dey uss ka iss kay baad koi chara saaz nahi aur tu dekhay ga kay zalim log azab ko dekh ker keh rahen hongay kay kiya wapis janey ki koi raah hai
  42,45,Aur tu enhen dekhay ga kay woh (jahannum kay) samney la-kharay kiyey jayen gay maray zillat kay jhukay jarahen hongay aur kan-ankhiyon say dekh rahey hongay eman walay saaf kahen gay kay haqeeqi ziyan kaar woh hain jinhon ney aaj qayamat kay din apnay aap ko aur apnay ghar walon ko nuksan mein dal diya. Yaad rakho kay yaqeenan zalim log daaeemi azab mein hain
  42,46,Unn kay koi madadgar nahi jo Allah Taalaa say alag unn ki madad ker saken aur jissay Allah gumrah kerdey uss kay liye koi raasta hi nahi
  42,47,Apnay rab ka hukum maan lo iss say pehlay kay Allah ki janib say woh din aajaye jiss ka hut jana na-mumkin hai tumhen uss roz na koi panah ki jagah milay gi na chup ker anjan bann janey ki
  42,48,Agar yeh mun pher len to hum ney aap ko inn per nigheybaan bana ker nahi bheja aap kay zimay to sirf paygham phoncha dena hai hum jab kabhi insan ko apni meharbani ka maza chakhatay hain to woh iss per itra jata hai aur agar unhen unn kay aemaal ki waja say koi museebat phonchti hai to be-shak insan bara hi na shukra hai
  42,49,Aasmano ki aur zamin ki saltanat Allah Taalaa hi kay liye hai woh jo chahata hai peda kerta hai jiss ko chahata hai betyian deta hai aur jissay chahata hai betay deta hai
  42,50,Ya enhen jama ker deta hai betay bhi aur betyian bhi aur jissay chahye baanjh ker deta hai woh baray ilm wala aur kamil qudrat wala hai